      "created_at": "2024-09-26T08:48:45.245Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Thanks, yes you can do this with our app now.  So it works fine for slopes.  But converting to ERG and automatic power control is something else.  Setting specific ERG values you can pedal on the flat at 100w or at 130w depending on how you feel.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/3/3c54d43db6cbedee1b23a6d34f3090b5a1e0169d.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/3c54d43db6cbedee1b23a6d34f3090b5a1e0169d\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3c54d43db6cbedee1b23a6d34f3090b5a1e0169d_2_690x412.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"8BIopfb7OmVB7BtQe8ZyucYLsAJ\" width=\"690\" height=\"412\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3c54d43db6cbedee1b23a6d34f3090b5a1e0169d_2_690x412.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3c54d43db6cbedee1b23a6d34f3090b5a1e0169d_2_1035x618.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3c54d43db6cbedee1b23a6d34f3090b5a1e0169d_2_1380x824.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"DAD8DA\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">2354\u00d71408 321 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>So slope mode is popular for some of our users.</p>\n<p>Here is a video</p><div class=\"youtube-onebox lazy-video-container\" data-video-id=\"MK87_Seu658\" data-video-title=\"Automatic Slope, ERG and HR mode switching.  How to create your workout in TrainerDay.\" data-video-start-time=\"\" data-provider-name=\"youtube\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MK87_Seu658\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"video-thumbnail\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <img class=\"youtube-thumbnail\" src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/5/5ed228140fe81fb6e7847d9cc45e890581a8a53d.jpeg\" title=\"Automatic Slope, ERG and HR mode switching.  How to create your workout in TrainerDay.\" data-dominant-color=\"8C8C90\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\">\n  </a>\n</div>\n",
